# Reports Directory

This folder is reserved for storing test execution reports generated by the automation framework.

---

## 📊 Purpose of This Folder

| Report Type | Purpose |
|-------------|--------|
| NUnit XML | Default test output for CI tools |
| HTML Reports (Planned) | Human-readable dashboards |
| ExtentReports (Planned) | BDD-style step logging and screenshots |
| Allure Reports (Optional) | Advanced trend and analytics reports |

---

## 🗂 Suggested Folder Naming

/Reports
/Run_2025-01-10_2030
/Run_2025-01-11_0930
latest/


---

## 🚀 Planned Report Integrations

| Tool | Status |
|------|--------|
| NUnit Console Logs | ✅ Available now |
| ExtentReports | 🔜 Planned (Phase 3) |
| GitHub Actions Artifacts | 🔜 Optional for CI/CD |
| Allure Report | 🟡 Optional for Advanced Setup |

---

## 💡 Tip

When using ExtentReports, configure output like:

./Reports/latest/index.html



This allows consistent links in CI pipelines or README.

---

## 📁 Example (Future)

Reports/
latest/
index.html # Main report file
screenshots/ # UI or API failure evidence
archive/
Run_2025-01-14_1022/

This folder stays empty until reporting tools are configured.